          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "At dawn, when Adi farmers in the Siang River valley rise to tend their jhum fields on the misty hillsides, pray that the Light of the World would break through the spiritual fog that has long covered this highland people.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
