    },
    {
      "id": 21579,
      "title": "",
      "language_code": "en",
      "content_json": {
        "type": "doc",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Kingdom Prayers",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "verse",
            "attrs": {
              "reference": "Matthew 9:37-38",
              "translation": "NKJV"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "37 ",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "superscript"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Then He said to His disciples, “The harvest truly is plentiful, but the laborers are few. ",
                    "type": "text"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "38 ",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "superscript"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Therefore pray the Lord of the harvest to send out laborers into His harvest.”",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "Pray for laborers among this people group: Jesus told us to pray that the Lord would raise up laborers (hard workers) for the harvest fields. Please pray that God would raise up missionaries from all over the world to plant the Church together among unreached people groups.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "content_date": "2026-03-01",
      "content_type": "static",
      "people_group_data": null
    },
    {
      "id": 9897,
      "title": "",
      "language_code": "en",
